---
title: Lentil & Porcini Mushroom Shepherd's Pie with Parmesan Mash Topping
description: Haven't found the umami you've been looking for? That elusive fifth ‘savoury’ flavour is bursting out of this pie thanks to the dried porcini mushrooms in the lentil filling and the Parmesan stirred through the creamy mash topping. Enjoy!
